_sText:
Fy_weaver-smash has several secrets..

1:  Press the use button on any of the white orbs for various effect

2:  Try standing on the white orb that cries like an eagle..  follow the arrows up top.  Jump to get past the barrier at the     second arrow..
    If you have made it this far-  careful-  only half the top edge of the map has a no-clip rail..  meaning on half u CAN FALL OFF :D
    Jump onto the stone step to teleport..

3:  Shoot the third barrel on the other side of the water...

4:  The blue teleport in between the two sets of steps?  Yes, just have momentum you needn't take any damage.

5:  To the left of number 4's teleport, you can jump off the THIRD row of boxes, at jusssssssst the right spot, and teleport outside :)
